{"tid":1495943,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[學術討論］又係時候溫下革命第一人-毛澤東嘅游擊思維","createTime":"2019-08-22T09:43:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T11:09:40.000Z","uid":67340,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1cca96d72c85ae982d5763dbddcc44ee3fec0a94","tid":1495943,"uid":67340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T09:43:02.000Z","msg":"毛毛連唔識字嘅草根莽夫都動員到，而且進退有序，就係靠呢個黃金口訣<br />\n<br />\n敵進我退，敵駐我擾，敵疲我打，敵退我追<br />\n<br />\n知你班連登仔平時唔用功讀書，字都唔識隻，同我mak 大雙眼睇清楚<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">敵進我退，敵駐我擾，敵疲我打，敵退我追</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">黑警藍蛆</span></span>對付抗爭者有冇手軟？有冇留手？<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">冇啊！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n依家就係敵疲我打嘅好時機，我地趁對方鋒芒漸減，就應全力升級，作長久之計，唔好妄想可以一蹴而就<br />\n<br />\n利申純學術討論，唔鼓勵大家犯法<br />\nRemember remember <br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r81JHQf.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr81JHQf.gif&h=2fbcfc67&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6fe168030ccb3fbccedd4b952c1345de56f57429","tid":1495943,"uid":67340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T09:43:19.000Z","msg":"自推十連發"},{"pid":"27be1855e96994205a19b1e4b0f2a41b4207302c","tid":1495943,"uid":235374,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T09:43:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">   敵疲我打 敵退我追 </span></span>"},{"pid":"45513a3fbc7e1aa16884a5a44a88f6f7ecbdf5e4","tid":1495943,"uid":67340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T09:43:30.000Z","msg":"Remember remember"},{"pid":"4da7bd2746d864ac78c89cf1cc5bc2c80fe0838d","tid":1495943,"uid":67340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T09:43:40.000Z","msg":"T